<promed@promedmail.org>

[There are a number of conflicting statements relating to this patient, and
as yet no positive evidence for identifying this as a case of vCJD, apart
from the young age of the patient. However, residence in the UK at the
beginning of the vCJD outbreak is a potential risk factor. - Mod.CP]
